They're not Laurel and Hardy, but Jack and Dave - as in Hanna and Letterman - have delivered a lot of laughs to late-night television audiences for three decades. Tonight is their final comedic duet. Letterman will bow out of television on May 20, and this is the last time that Hanna and a parade of animals will appear on his show.
